Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.08,SignB,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\p1\c&HFEFEFE&\fscx216\fscy69\pos(1132.5,907.5)}m 0 0 l 150 0 150 150 0 150{\p0}
